<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Part of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">stele</rs> broken away above and below (<measure dim="height" unit="metre" type="length">0.30</measure> x <measure dim="width" unit="metre" type="length">0.41</measure> x <measure dim="depth" unit="metre" type="length">0.18</measure>). There are traces of a decorated panel above.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on one face within a plain raised border (panel <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.33</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.21</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>0.02, perhaps first century A. D; square sigma; there is a stop after every word, except καί.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date exact="none" cert="low" notAfter="0100" notBefore="0001">First century A. D.</date>
 (<rs type="criteria">prosopography</rs>)</p>
</div>
